---
title: Smart Ground Beef Parmesan-Style Patties with Veggie Medley and Potatoes
description: Featuring ground beef patties smothered in marinara sauce and melted cheese, this dinner offers all the comforts of classic Parmesan. For your sides, potatoes, peppers and zucchini are roasted and finished with Parmesan and parsley.
